legs.end_address: Mehmetpaşa, Atatürk Blv. 1 D, 58040 Sivas Merkez/Sivas, Turkey
legs.start_address: Çarşı, Bahriye Üçok Cd. No:1, 08000 Artvin Merkez/Artvin, Turkey

steps.html_instructions: Head northwest on Bahriye Üçok Cd. toward Cumhuriyet Cd.
Turn right onto Çağal Sk.
Turn right onto Koru Sk.
Sharp right at Esentepe Sk.
Turn left onto Miralay Şükrü Bey Cd.
Miralay Şükrü Bey Cd. turns slightly left and becomes Zeytin Sk.
Turn left onto Fevzi Çakmak Cd.
Turn right onto Erzurum Cd./D010/D950

At the roundabout, take the 1st exit onto Erzurum Artvin Yolu/D950
Continue to follow D950

Take the ramp onto Kars-Erzincan Yolu/D100
Continue to follow D100
Turn left onto Sivas Erzincan Yolu/D100/E80
Take the exit on the left toward Sivas Erzincan Yolu
Keep right at the fork to continue toward Sivas Erzincan Yolu
Turn right onto Sivas Erzincan Yolu
Take the ramp to Sivas Erzincan Yolu/D200/E88

Continue onto Sivas Erzincan Yolu/D200/E88
Continue to follow D200/E88
Take the exit toward M. Fethi Akyüz Cd.
Keep right at the fork and merge onto M. Fethi Akyüz Cd.
Continue onto Atatürk Blv.

Enter the roundabout
Destination will be on the left
